Last Broadcast Date: Thu 6 Sep 2012
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world: today Matthew Bannister meets a Swedish cartoonist with a bounty on his head after caricaturing the Prophet Muhammed; also the failed comedian who joined the British Marines as a bet and ended up in Afghanistan; and the Guatemalan volunteers who go to the office in the day and fight fires in the night. Show less